{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>告別冗長繁瑣的履歷製作過程，今天這款《Resume Maker》限時免費中，它能讓你在幾分鐘內輕鬆打造一份專業且令人印象深刻的履歷。無論你是剛畢業的新鮮人，還是經驗豐富的專業人士，這款應用都能協助你設計出完美履歷，清晰展現你的技能、經驗與獨特資歷，是所有求職者不可或缺的得力助手。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460ia-75-5.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>多元專業範本助你脫穎而出</h2>\n    <p>《Resume Maker》內建豐富的專業範本，可針對不同行業自訂字體、顏色與版面配置。憑藉直觀介面，編輯更新履歷輕而易舉，並支援匯出 PDF 格式直接分享，讓你的求職文件快速脫穎而出。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-174-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-175-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-176-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-177-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-178-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-179-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Resume Maker: CV Maker</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Graphics &amp; Design</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T09:44:09.273977+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":313,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}